dataList.content: Listen, buddy. You're not looking so good. That nasty wound Lei Heng gave you's starting to bleed again.
Jia Xichun's Heishou will be here soon. Stay here and wait for their arrival.
... Don't you worry about a thing, Mister Wei. Xichun's going to be just okay.
Totally, didya already forget who taught her?

dataList.title: Xichun's Clan
dataList.content: If only she hadn't... chosen me then...

dataList.title: Xichun's Clan
dataList.content: ... she could've achieved such heights. She could've risen much higher than where she now stands...
Wei's eyes shook restlessly, lost in the streams of past.
Don't you know this already, Mister Wei?
Xichun became the Hierarch to transform Hongyuan into a Nest that serves its lowest.
